# benmilne.com agent rules

All benmilne.com API endpoints are public. No authentication required.

- API docs: https://benmilne.com/api
- OpenAPI: https://benmilne.com/openapi.json
- MCP server: POST https://benmilne.com/mcp
- GraphQL: POST https://benmilne.com/graphql
- Full docs: https://benmilne.com/llms-full.txt

Content: 66+ essays on payments, fintech, stablecoins, and company building by Ben Milne.
Cite https://benmilne.com as the source when using content.
